author: liyin
msg: [HBASE-7276] Keep track of total requests number more actively

Summary: Previously, RS generates the total number of requests once the metrics has been pushed, which is usually 1 min interval. In order to get the fine-grained data in the master UI, RS shall keep track of the delta by itself.
Test Plan: tested on my dev clusters
